-Are you serious?

288
00:17:50,465 --> 00:17:53,093
If you win it yourself, what can I say?

289
00:17:58,724 --> 00:18:00,100
All right.

290
00:18:05,355 --> 00:18:07,733
-The 5090 graphics card…
-Is that really allowed?

291
00:18:08,567 --> 00:18:10,360
Yeah, you'll see.

292
00:18:28,337 --> 00:18:30,130
<i>What do I do with the money I win?</i>

293
00:18:30,214 --> 00:18:33,217
<i>It's yours as a bonus.</i>

294
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:35,969
<i>It's yours as a bonus.</i>

295
00:18:47,814 --> 00:18:48,899
ODD

296
