322
00:21:02,115 --> 00:21:03,325
Hello.

323
00:21:03,408 --> 00:21:05,410
I've got a friend who needs some cash.

324
00:21:06,119 --> 00:21:07,579
Yes, about a million won?

325
00:21:08,955 --> 00:21:11,666
He says he'll lend it to you,
but he needs some collateral.

326
00:21:12,250 --> 00:21:13,502
-Collateral?
-Nothing big.

327
00:21:13,585 --> 00:21:16,004
-Just your parents' numbers.
-My parents' numbers?

328
00:21:16,088 --> 00:21:17,589
It's just a formality.

329
00:21:17,672 --> 00:21:20,384
We're not going to lose anyway.
Martingale, remember?

330
00:21:27,265 --> 00:21:29,851
But didn't you say it was a million won?

331
00:21:29,935 --> 00:21:31,645
I only received 800,000 won.

332
00:21:31,728 --> 00:21:33,397
Upfront interest, dumbass.

333
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,690
He takes 20% and gives you the rest.

334
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:41,154
The interest rate is 3% per day.

335
00:21:41,238 --> 00:21:43,156
For 1,000,000 won, 3% is 30,000 won.

336
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:48,370
The next day, it's not 3% of 1,000,000 won
but 3% of 1,030,000 won after interest.

337
00:21:48,453 --> 00:21:50,414
It's calculated as compound interest.

338
00:21:51,289 --> 00:21:52,541
After a month,

339
00:21:53,041 --> 00:21:57,003
800,000 won becomes 2,427,243 won.

340
00:21:57,838 --> 00:22:02,467
And after 100 days,
it becomes 19,218,364 won.

341
00:22:04,302 --> 00:22:09,182
After a year,
it becomes 48,482,008,003 won.

342
00:22:10,016 --> 00:22:11,268
You did well. Okay?

343
00:22:11,351 --> 00:22:13,270
Good job. Well done.

344
00:22:13,353 --> 00:22:19,025
Deputy Bong, my man. You lost big time,
so they'll come down on you soon.

345
00:22:19,776 --> 00:22:21,027
